original_title: Praying Mantis Man: Or how I faced off against the fearsome Clavicle Crusher
overview: A man who has an irrational fear of praying mantises takes it upon himself to use what frightens him to become a "superhero". But soon he has to face off against his first supervillain, the revenge fueled CLAVICLE CRUSHER.
tagline: A broken clavicle can change everything.
title: Praying Mantis Man: Or how I faced off against the fearsome Clavicle Crusher
